org.bytedeco.pytorch

Class InputArchive

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.pytorch.InputArchive
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    @Namespace(value="torch::serialize")
 @NoOffset
 @Properties(inherit=torch.class)
public class InputArchive
extends Pointer
    A recursive representation of tensors that can be deserialized from a file or stream. In most cases, users should not have to interact with this class, and should instead use torch::load.
